## Document ID: SOP-ONDREJ-001 | PRD-ONDREJ-001
## Date: 2026-05-20 | Owner: Viktor Chief of Staff | Approved by: Rashida Mendes

---

## 1. Executive Summary

Integrate 7 open-source resources from the David Ondrej × Michael Shimeles agentic engineering ecosystem into InsightProfit's tech stack. These resources fill 2 major gaps (AEO visibility tracking, phone agents), upgrade 2 existing systems (agent dispatch, codebase engineering), and add 3 new capability patterns (shopping checkout, local LLM, lead-magnet funnels).

**Total new assets:**
- 1 new Viktor Space app (`aeo.insightprofit.live`)
- 3 new skills (vapi_phone_agents, agent_shopping_checkout, aeo_platform)
- 2 skill upgrades (codebase_engineering, agent_dispatch_bridge)
- 1 reference addition (token_optimization)
- 1 new weekly cron
- 1 new Command Center sidebar view

**Estimated build time:** 3-5 days across 3 phases
**Estimated cost:** ~$0/mo ongoing (self-hosted, free-tier APIs)

---

## 2. Scope & Phasing

### Phase 1: Knowledge Merges (Day 1-2)
Zero-code skill updates. Merge battle-tested methodologies into our existing skills.

| Task | Target | Source |
|------|--------|--------|
| Merge 7-step workflow | `skills/codebase_engineering/` | micky-podcast-agentic-engineering |
| Add source-code-context convention | `skills/codebase_engineering/` | micky-podcast-agentic-engineering |
| Add cleanup pass protocol | `skills/codebase_engineering/` | micky-podcast-agentic-engineering |
| Upgrade review-fix loop | `skills/codebase_engineering/` + `skills/verifier_agent/` | micky-podcast-agentic-engineering |
| Add service-layer architecture ref | `skills/codebase_engineering/` | michaelshimeles/skills |
| Add Hermes-CEO handoff protocol | `skills/agent_dispatch_bridge/` | Hermes-CEO |
| Add known-friction docs | `skills/agent_dispatch_bridge/` | Hermes-CEO |
| Create Vapi phone agents skill | `skills/vapi_phone_agents/` | vapi-phone-agent-use-cases |
| Create shopping checkout skill | `skills/agent_shopping_checkout/` | agent-shopping-safe-checkout |
| Add local LLM reference | `skills/token_optimization/` | local-llm-picker-skill |

